{"tid":1813581,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"［急］有無人可以借設備畀我去台北搞流動放映會","createTime":"2020-01-06T11:24:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T23:48:43.000Z","uid":32932,"like":32,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"7ff8b6d89ab288a3064d4144c88002c75ff6c48d","tid":1813581,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T11:24:23.000Z","msg":"見到流亡台灣手足好驚韓國瑜會贏<br />\n加上台中韓國瑜造勢大會真係唔少野<br />\n決定做啲嘢幫吓手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n覺得放映會係一個好好既媒介去畀台灣人知道香港既情況<br />\n比起圖片同文字 片段取進好多<br />\n不過我無設備 又唔想買 睇過價錢要戶外用到都有啲貴 啲錢我寧願捐去612/直接畀流亡台灣義士做生活費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以想問大家借projector、screen同喇叭去台灣<br />\n想星期三晚出發 搞星期四、五、六 三日（未買機票）<br />\n有無人可以借上述設備畀我 同埋有無巴絲打呢幾日會去台北可以幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果唔信我既話 可以畀低押金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申未試過做呢啲野 淨係上個月去台北有舉牌叫人投票<br />\n<br />\ntg：taipei111<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/taipei111\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftaipei111&d=bwUHcV0Pscj1NrVo4Cy%2FDXwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=26076e87\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/taipei111</a>"},{"pid":"47e655891ba63c461d2b2f0ffb47a12bbd828854","tid":1813581,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T11:24:32.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"dddab729a68459b2e861eebcdf3093ae86f320b4","tid":1813581,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T1